name: Jay Darlington
description: '''Jay Peter Darlington''' (born 3 May 1968) is an English keyboardist, best known as a member of [[Kula Shaker]]. He went on to work as a touring member of [[Oasis (band)|Oasis]] was part of [[Totnes]], [[Devon]] based [[Progressive rock|prog]] band Magic Bus. and re-joined Kula Shaker in late 2022 as a full time member, during their recording of their seventh album, ''Natural Magick'' (2024), replacing Harry Broadbent.
